Package: dolt
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Git for Data - MySQL-compatible SQL database
 Dolt is a MySQL-compatible SQL database with Git-like version control.
 It provides branch, merge, diff, clone, push, and pull on SQL tables.
 .
 This package contains the dolt command line tool and SQL server.

Package: dolt-server
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, dolt (= ${binary:Version}), systemd
Description: Dolt SQL Server as a systemd service
 This package provides the systemd service configuration for running
 Dolt SQL Server as a system service.
